<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Application::_loadConfig detects content type based on extension. It looks for .yaml, but needs to also look for .yml, a common YAML extension.</p>

<p>current:</p>

<p>case 'yaml':
                $config = new Zend_Config_Yaml($file, $environment);
                break;</p>

<p>fix:</p>

<p>case 'yaml':
case 'yml':
                $config = new Zend_Config_Yaml($file, $environment);
                break;</p>

    </div>
